                     <interp inst="t18390916-2590-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18390916-2590-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp>for stealing, on the <rs id="t18390916-cd-174" type="crimeDate">
                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18390916-2590-offence-1 t18390916-cd-174"></join>17th of Sep<lb></lb>tember</rs>, 1 sovereign, and 9 shillings, the monies of <persName id="t18390916-name-1007" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18390916-name-1007" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18390916-name-1007" type="surname" value="PANK"></interp>
